  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project is fully funded by FORGE Funders for $200,000.
This project works with The Instituto Centroamericano de Estudios Fiscales, Tax Justice Network Africa and Christian Aid to carry out a 12-month project that centers on revealing and challenging the role of private creditors in hindering People&#x2019;s Recoveries to enhance the urgency with which the international community must address sovereign debt crises. The project will carry out research, campaigns and advocacy work internationally.</narrative>
